@startuml
actor Developer
participant "VS Code Editor" as Editor
participant "FlowViewProvider" as Webview
participant "Frank Framework\n(XSLT / Saxon)" as Saxon

Developer -> Editor : Opens XML file
Editor -> Webview : resolveWebviewView()
Webview -> Editor : Requests document text
Editor --> Webview : XML content
Webview -> Saxon : Transforms XML (adapter2mermaid.xsl)
Saxon --> Webview : Mermaid syntax
Webview -> Webview : Generate HTML with Mermaid syntax
Webview -> Editor : Update Webview HTML
Editor --> Developer : Shows visual diagram
@enduml